subject: One of those mindbenders...
author: lisbyfarrum
full_text:
I'm still going through last weekend's session.

The latest mind-blowing transmission was not only heard (in part) in
real time, but contains that name David, the mysterious Seven, and
Frank's Purple, which seem to be used as words to assure me I am
getting them, not anything random. At least, that's what I am hearing.

Just because things are so jammed in the file section, I only included
the 25 percent speed reduced version. Nothing else was done to this clip.

Ann
